import React from 'react'
import Banner from '../Components/Banner'
import Hero from '../Components/Hero'

const Register = () => {
    return (
        <Hero>
            <Banner
          title="Register"
          subtitle="Create Your Account"
        >
            <label>Name</label>
            <input type="text"/>
        </Banner>
        </Hero>
    )
}

export default Register
